lines.text: O Lord God, to whom vengeance belongs
O God, to whom vengeance belongs
And rise up, O King of the earth
Lord rise up, O Klng of the earth
How long will the wicked triumph?
How long will the wicked triumph?
Bles'd is the man whom You instruct
Oh Lord, and teach of Your law
That You may give him rest in his day of trouble
That You may give him rest in his day of adversity
Your mercy O Lord will hold me up
In my many troubles Your comfort delights my soul
